v2.0.6 - 20.06.2026
- Stage single DEBs before sharing so destination apps open reliably.
- Launch dpkg directly through sudo and reject duplicate concurrent installs.
- Open Filza before completing its custom share activity.

v2.0.5 - 19.06.2026
- Publish CLI and GUI in the Tweaks section for modern package managers.
- Share multiple rebuilt packages as one ZIP archive with byte-based progress.
- Install vnode-backed DEBs reliably on RootHide from the first request.

v2.0.0 - 17.11.2022
- Fully rewritten. Remove all the old bullshit under the hood.
- Start migrating to library and cli packages.
- Add options to change deb compression type and level. Now supports gzip, zstd and xz types.
- Improve logging system.
- Add some colors to cli commands errors.

v1.0.0 - 30.11.2020
Initial release.
- Supports list, leaves, export/import, rebuild packages commands. Written in a hurry.
